\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n點練，有無教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />&lt;/blockquote&gt;<br />\n<br />\n自己一個練就可以試下對住啲牆不停咁射再控實，試過咁練球感真係好左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n街場班人唔識防守<br />\n仲有其實所謂扭波勁其實都係屈變速<br />\n你唔主動搶佢根本唔會俾佢扭過"},{"pid":"49cd438ca7e506fd26a29e3d1a6b6a1191686ef7","tid":11211,"uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T16:59:05.000Z","msg":"練左右變速 插一下花再轉方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老實講 做傳波開心過自己扭<br />\n你傳波快狠準 多啲人會鍾意同你踢<br />\n跟隊都搵埋你 好過死扭爛扭"},{"pid":"be4e6046dd1041f8e3b2a852589017c85fab06eb","tid":11211,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:04:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多真係好撚勁<br />\n成日諗英超d人再勁好撚多好恐怖</blockquote><br />\n西甲再勁好撚好撚多"},{"pid":"c57c1a6442173d6653675db6c484ebbbba5f9fea","tid":11211,"uid":30476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>練左右變速 插一下花再轉方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 老實講 做傳波開心過自己扭<br />\n你傳波快狠準 多啲人會鍾意同你踢<br />\n跟隊都搵埋你 好過死扭爛扭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n基本上你扭波係幫人協防<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c7c1d6dd3c91fe839817168f15d5df9c1f8e0b8","tid":11211,"uid":1682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T17:18:39.000Z","msg":"細個踢波覺得扭過左人好有成功感 而家大左就覺得比到球靚直線 交到個靚助攻有更大成功感"},{"pid":"4c6c811a3d63a368c301842a8dabec8b49ce9ba1","tid":11211,"uid":33073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T18:33:59.000Z","msg":"Why not both, 扭完都橫傳比空晒既隊友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/a