quote><br />\n<br />\nThx 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b72c34725428a383f3debeb8ba143481ef5d914","tid":11211,"uid":43978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T11:54:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>踢中場多，cool 波比波唔差，但就係唔識過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打我同你差唔多，比波、意識都唔廢，但係盤球真係垃圾。好多時就因為盤球唔夠好，令到自己係場上少左一種創造力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n同埋你可以上youtube search&quot;Become Elite &quot; 呢個channel 全部都係足球訓練嘅片，有啲係關於dribbling <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解踢中場要盤球？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇啲頂級中場kroos ozil xavi都係好少過人<br />\n利申：踢中場踢過下uteam區隊"},{"pid":"54fa47163645fccf2e3f4e8dbf4618be7a86c6e2","tid":11211,"uid":37660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:01:47.000Z","msg":"個人覺得扭波點都唔夠比波快<br />\n當然識就最好啦，但係唔識又點 ？識踢配合小組一樣踢到好波"},{"pid":"5104a26e7941bc588434ddea8ae3975516baf494","tid":11211,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:54:10.000Z","msg":"練好控波，傳波係街場已經夠做。<br />\n<br />\n街場個場咁細俾你扭過一個都好快有另一個後衛埋到黎，或者龍門，扭失左即刻變左俾人反攻，本來攻上去既隊友要即刻回防，晒撚晒隊友d體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75768fce71d69d1aac3e1822de457d03d3f1bee5","tid":11211,"uid":33073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-30T12:57:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>踢中場多，cool 波比波唔差，但就係唔識過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br 